<anchor n="T.50.2061.0789b11"/><head>習禪篇論</head><p xml:id="pT50p0789b1101"><lb
n="0789b11" ed="T"/>論曰：梵語「禪那<ptr type="glossary" target="#g227"/>」，華言「念修」也。以其觸情念<lb
n="0789b12" ed="T"/>而無念<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1133"/>，終日修而無修<ptr target="#n1134"/>。又云「正定<ptr type="glossary" target="#g199"/>」也，「正受」<lb 
n="0789b13" ed="T"/>也。正則廓然<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1135"/>冥而定矣。正受簡邪思惟、增遍<lb
n="0789b14" ed="T"/>計故<ptr target="#n1137"/>。所以「奢摩他<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1138"/>」以寂靜故，「三摩提<ptr type="glossary" target="#g199"/>」以觀如<lb
n="0789b15" ed="T"/><anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz1"/>幻<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz1"/>故，若「禪那」者，俱離靜<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz2"/>幻<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz2"/>故，始云：「菩薩不<lb
n="0789b16" ed="T"/>住此岸，不住彼岸，而度眾生令登彼岸<ptr target="#n1139"/>。」<lb
n="0789b17" ed="T"/>也。若然者，諸聖住處既如彼，諸聖度生復若<lb
n="0789b18" ed="T"/>何？</p><p>稽夫法演<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢</placeName>庭，極證之名未著；風行<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬<lb
n="0789b19" ed="T"/>阜</placeName><ptr target="#n1140"/>，禪那之學始萌。<persName key="A000436">佛陀什</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000048176">秦</placeName>擯而來<ptr target="#n1141"/>；<persName key="A004683">般若多</persName><ptr target="#n1142"/>，<lb
n="0789b20" ed="T"/><date from-iso="0317-04-07" key="j18369381874651" to-iso="0420-07-08">晉朝</date>而至，時<persName key="A001204">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>也，密傳坐法，深斡玄機，漸<lb
n="0789b21" ed="T"/>染施行，依違<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1143"/>祖述。<placeName key="PL000000000101">吳</placeName>之<persName key="A001046">僧會</persName>亦示有緣，俱未<lb
n="0789b22" ed="T"/>分明，肆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1144"/>多隱祕。及乎<persName key="A009599">慧文<roleName>大士</roleName></persName>，肇尋<persName key="A001482">龍樹</persName><lb
n="0789b23" ed="T"/>之宗；<persName key="A001711">思</persName>大禪翁，繼傳三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>之妙。<persName key="A001301">天台智者</persName>引<lb
n="0789b24" ed="T"/>而伸之，化導<date from-iso="0557-11-18" key="j19248221936231" to-iso="0589-02-12">陳</date>、<date from-iso="0581-03-06" key="j19333311946884" to-iso="0618-04-15">隋</date>，名題「止觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g187"/>」。粵有<placeName key="PL000000048208">中天</placeName><persName key="A001361">達<lb
n="0789b25" ed="T"/>磨</persName>，哀我群生，知梵夾之雖傳，為名相之所<lb
n="0789b26" ed="T"/>溺，認指忘月<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1145"/>，得魚執筌<ptr target="#n1146"/>，但矜誦念<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz3"/>以<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz3"/>為<lb
n="0789b27" ed="T"/>功，不信<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz4"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz4"/>躬之是佛。是以倡言曰：「<ref type="person" target="A001361">吾</ref>直指<lb
n="0789b28" ed="T"/>人心，見性成佛，不立文字<ptr target="#n1147"/>也。」此乃乘方便<lb
n="0789b29" ed="T"/>波羅蜜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1124"/>，徑直而度，免無量之迂迴焉。嗟乎！經
<pb n="0789c" xml:id="T50.2061.0789c" ed="T"/><lb
n="0789c01" ed="T"/>有曲指，曲指則漸修也<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1148"/>。見性成佛者，頓悟<lb
n="0789c02" ed="T"/>自心本來清淨，元無煩惱，無漏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g432"/>智性，本自具<lb
n="0789c03" ed="T"/>足。此心即佛，畢了無異。如此修證，是最上<lb
n="0789c04" ed="T"/>乘禪也。「不立文字」者，經云：「不著文字，不離<lb
n="0789c05" ed="T"/>文字。非無文字，能如是修，不見修相也。<ptr target="#n1149"/>」<lb
n="0789c06" ed="T"/>又<persName key="A001361">達磨</persName>立法，要唯二種，謂理也、行也。然則直<lb
n="0789c07" ed="T"/>而不<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz5"/>迂<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz5"/>，不速而疾，云不立文字，乃反權合<lb
n="0789c08" ed="T"/>道也<ptr target="#n1150"/>。爾時<persName key="A002098">梁武</persName>不知，<placeName key="PL000000000130">魏</placeName>人未重，向<placeName key="PL000000023255">少林</placeName>而<lb
n="0789c09" ed="T"/>面壁，唯<persName key="A003881">慧可</persName>以神交。亦猶《白雪》雖歌，<placeName key="PL000000037154">巴</placeName>童<lb
n="0789c10" ed="T"/>寡和<ptr target="#n1151"/>。後則<ptr target="#n1163"/>臨<placeName key="PL000000056121">汧</placeName>牧圉<ptr target="#n1162"/>，子孫終號於強<placeName key="PL000000000096">秦</placeName>；避<lb
n="0789c11" ed="T"/>狄<placeName key="PL000000042907">岐<anchor xml:id="beg0789002"/>邠<anchor xml:id="end0789002"/></placeName><ptr target="#n1152"/>，<persName key="A002160">文</persName>、<persName key="A002432">武</persName>乃成其王道。<persName key="A003881">可</persName>生<persName key="A001601">璨</persName>，<persName key="A001601">璨</persName>生<lb
n="0789c12" ed="T"/><persName key="A003654">信</persName>。<persName key="A003654">信</persName>下分二枝，一<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>、二<persName key="A003867">融</persName>。<persName key="A003867">融</persName>，<persName key="A003867">牛頭</persName>也。<persName key="A000237">忍</persName>生<lb
n="0789c13" ed="T"/><persName key="A009582">秀</persName>與<persName key="A001719">能</persName>。<persName key="A001719">能</persName>傳信衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1212"/>，若諸侯付子孫之分器<ptr type="glossary" target="#g176"/><lb
n="0789c14" ed="T"/>也，厥後此宗越盛焉。蔭車百輛，尼拘樹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1164"/>而展<lb
n="0789c15" ed="T"/>轉垂枝；施雨萬方，<persName key="A013630">阿耨龍</persName>而連筵布潤。當<lb
n="0789c16" ed="T"/>是時也，應其懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>，屬于此人，後來得道無<lb
n="0789c17" ed="T"/>央數<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1166"/>是歟！</p><p>重之曰：「夫禪之為物也，其大矣<lb
n="0789c18" ed="T"/>哉！<ptr target="#n1168"/>」諸佛得之昇等<ptr type="glossary" target="#g26"/>、妙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1169"/>，雌龍<ptr target="#n1167"/>得之破障<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1170"/>、纏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1171"/>，率<lb
n="0789c19" ed="T"/>由<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1175"/>速疾之門無過此。故今之像<ptr type="glossary" target="#g184"/>末，鬪諍復<lb
n="0789c20" ed="T"/>生，師足既傷，資<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1172"/>爭未<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>己</sic><corr>已</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz6"/>。如聞此心是佛，便<lb
n="0789c21" ed="T"/>言三十二相<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1213"/>何無？或聞一路涅槃，則曰八<lb
n="0789c22" ed="T"/>萬法門<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1214"/>何在？曾不知經中發菩提心，此見<lb
n="0789c23" ed="T"/>佛性也。云何修菩薩行，此行布<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1215"/>修行也。因<lb
n="0789c24" ed="T"/>信不及，無明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1173"/>所迷，溺喪忘歸，何由復業！或<lb
n="0789c25" ed="T"/>舉經以示之，則對曰：「此性宗法。」或謂之曰：<lb
n="0789c26" ed="T"/>「莫是魔說，還可焚毀否？」且置而勿論。又欲<lb
n="0789c27" ed="T"/>棄之，又欲存之，不其惑乎？昔者<placeName key="PL000000047993">于闐</placeName>諸<lb
n="0789c28" ed="T"/>部謂《道行經》<ptr target="#n1174"/>為婆羅門書<ptr target="#n1176"/>，<placeName key="PL000000048336">烏<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>茶</sic><corr>荼</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz7"/></placeName>小乘謗大<lb
n="0789c29" ed="T"/>乘學作空<anchor xml:id="beg0789sgsz8"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0789sgsz8"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1177"/>外道<ptr target="#n1178"/>。<placeName key="PL000000048207">西乾</placeName>尚爾，此何驚乎？良以
<pb n="0790a" xml:id="T50.2061.0790a" ed="T"/><lb
n="0790a01" ed="T"/>六代宗師，一期<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1179"/>舉唱，但破百年之暗，靡營一<lb
n="0790a02" ed="T"/>室之隳。殊不知禪有理焉，禪有行焉。脫或<ptr type="glossary" target="#g484"/><lb
n="0790a03" ed="T"/>戒乘俱急<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1180"/>，目足<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1181"/>更資，行不廢而理逾明，法無<lb
n="0790a04" ed="T"/>偏而功兼濟。然後<anchor xml:id="beg0790001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>如</sic><corr>始</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0790001"/>可與言禪<anchor xml:id="beg0790sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>己</sic><corr>已</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0790sgsz1"/>矣<ptr target="#n1182"/>。其<lb
n="0790a05" ed="T"/>如玄學多斥講家，目為數寶之人，終困<lb
n="0790a06" ed="T"/>屢空<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1183"/>之室。那不見經是佛言，禪是佛意，諸佛<lb
n="0790a07" ed="T"/>心口，定不相違。施設<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1184"/>逗根<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1185"/>，用有時處。況以<lb
n="0790a08" ed="T"/>經江高國紀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1186"/>之名，論海總朝宗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1187"/>之會。毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>一<lb
n="0790a09" ed="T"/>學，軌範千途<ptr target="#n1188"/>。授形俱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1189"/>築釋子之基，唱隨行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1190"/><lb
n="0790a10" ed="T"/>淨沙門之業，擬捐三事<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1191"/>，何駕一乘？終包不<lb
n="0790a11" ed="T"/>足之羞，豈<anchor xml:id="beg0790sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>倒</sic><corr>到</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0790sgsz2"/>轉依之地<ptr type="glossary" target="#g633"/>？通人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1192"/>不誚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1193"/>，豎子<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1194"/>何<lb 
n="0790a12" ed="T"/>知？佛事門中不捨一法，吠聲貽責，遷怒傷<lb
n="0790a13" ed="T"/>人，因擊鼠以破盆，為爭摶而噬主，自他<lb
n="0790a14" ed="T"/>俱有，彼我須均，縱橫盡而成一秦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1195"/>，氣劑和而<lb
n="0790a15" ed="T"/>成一味者也。今從<date from-iso="0627-01-26" key="j19500922132856" to-iso="1127-06-18">貞觀及于宋朝</date>，於山<lb
n="0790a16" ed="T"/>選山，露<placeName key="PL000000055454">須彌</placeName>而出海；於羽求羽，放金翅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g617"/><lb
n="0790a17" ed="T"/>以騰空。令其鑽仰之儔，慕此堅高之道矣。<lb
n="0790a18" ed="T"/>吾徒通達，無相奪倫，譬若文武是一人之藝，<lb
n="0790a19" ed="T"/>不能兼者，互相非斥耳。若相推重，佛法增<lb
n="0790a20" ed="T"/>明，酬君王度<anchor xml:id="beg0790sgsz3"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0790sgsz3"/>之恩，答我佛為師之訓。慎<lb
n="0790a21" ed="T"/>之哉！慎之哉！</p>
</div>